Url.Title: Getting Started With Web Admin Configuration Tool
Url.Abstract: Getting Started With Web Admin Configuration Tool Web Admin Configuration Tool is available on your server under Start > All Programs > Absolute Manage > Web Admin Configuration Tool.

Url.Title: Managing AM Servers in Your Web Admin Installation
Url.Abstract: Managing AM Servers in Your Web Admin Installation You can use Web Admin Configuration Tool to view a list of existing AM Servers registered in your Web Admin installation, register new AM Servers, and set a default AM Server for your Self-Service Portal user logins.
